title: Digimon Frontier
overview: Takuya, Kouji, Izumi, Junpei. and Tomoki meet each other on a train that takes them to the Digital World where a war against evil is being fought. The Angel digimon, Cherubimon, one of the three angels sent to save the world from the power-hungry Lucemon, has turned to the dark side and the entire Digital World is in peril. To fight this great battle, the five CHOSEN ONES must find the Densetsu no Spirit (Legendary Spirit).
